HEADWORD: Understatement
<hw>Un"der*state`ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of
understating, or the condition of being understated; that which is
understated; a statement below the truth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

